    <h1>Day 20 of 100 Days of Web Development</h1>

    <p>
        Today I learned how to group form elements using
        fieldset and legend in HTML.
    </p>

    <form>
        <fieldset>
            <legend>Personal Information</legend>

            <label>
                Name:
                <input type="text">
            </label>
            <br><br>

            <label>
                Email:
                <input type="email">
            </label>
        </fieldset>
    </form>

